            <title>華為撞 Apple 於同一日舉行發布會，餘承東：將發布華為巔峯之作</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/huawei-29/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-29</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/huawei-29/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 08:03:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[餘承東]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[摺疊式螢幕]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[華為]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1260055</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 剛宣佈將於香港時間 9 月 10 日凌晨 1 時舉行秋季發布會，而華為亦緊隨其後宣佈於 9 月 10 日舉行發布會，兩大發布會將於同日舉行。</p><p>華為終端今（2 日）宣佈，華為見非凡品牌盛典及鴻蒙智行新品發布會將於 9 月 10 日 14 時 30 分舉行。華為董事餘承東表示，屆時將帶來華為最具引領性、創新性、顛覆性的產品。他又指經過 5 年的堅持及投入，華為將意想不到的劃時代產品由科幻變成現實，稱大家可期待即將發布的華為巔峯之作。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_ebd04964f7804635b9.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_ebd04964f7804635b9-430x580.jpg" alt="" width="430" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_ebd04964f7804635b9-430x580.jpg 430w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_ebd04964f7804635b9.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 430px" /></a></p><p>早前餘承東曾在科技公司與輝同行的直播中透露，下代華為摺疊式螢幕經過 5 年研發後即將面世，指這款摺疊式螢幕別人想得到但做不出來。</p><p>根據網上流傳的相片可見，餘承東曾在一部三摺疊式螢幕的新裝置使用微信，左邊螢幕為訊息列表，而右邊則是對話框。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_e5dc36e698984eb3a0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260057" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_e5dc36e698984eb3a0-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_e5dc36e698984eb3a0-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_e5dc36e698984eb3a0.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_5b1710a57fff4c55b3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_5b1710a57fff4c55b3-552x580.jpg" alt="" width="552" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_5b1710a57fff4c55b3-552x580.jpg 552w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_5b1710a57fff4c55b3.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 552px" /></a></p><p>圖片來源：快科技</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1000/1000757.htm">快科技</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/01/huawei-harmony-os-next-beta/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">多款手機平板合資格，華為 HarmonyOS NEXT 開放大範圍測試</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/25/huawei-watch-d2-blood-pressure-sept/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為 Watch D2 傳 9 月發表，將提供血壓計、心電圖功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/huawei-matepad-air-launch-china/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">纖薄全金屬機身配大容量電池，華為 MatePad Air (2024) 中國發表</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/huawei-29/mobile-phone/">華為撞 Apple 於同一日舉行發布會，餘承東：將發布華為巔峯之作</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
